<subSubSection box="[197,1193,1769,1793]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,1157,1901]" box="[197,1193,1769,1793]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,331,1769,1793]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" reason="1">Etymology.</emphasis>
The name is descriptive for the 3 medial spines on the shaft of the aedeagus.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
